  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Pet Groomer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage the day-to-day business operations of grooming.</li><li>Ensure pet grooming equipments are well maintained.</li><li>Perform pet grooming based on the best practices and customers’ needs</li><li>Ensure workplace safety, hygiene level and cleanliness of the grooming centre.</li><li>Perform general housekeeping to maintain a safe and hygienic environment for staff, customers and pets.</li><li>Ensure safety of pets throughout the grooming process.</li><li>Ensure that all pets are well taken care of and in compliance with AVS guidelines.</li><li>Highlight abnormalities of pets to the customers to avoid unnecessary conflicts or misunderstanding.</li><li>Clip or file pet’s nails</li><li>Perform ear-cleaning services</li><li>Any other ad hoc duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min 1 years of industry experience in grooming dogs</li><li>Hand shearing and scissoring skills</li><li>Comfort working with various breeds of dogs</li><li>Good Communication skills</li><li>Patience & Reliabilty</li><li>Must love dogs/cats</li></ul>",
